Fixed by adding `(window-parameters . ((dedicated . t)))` to the `display-buffer-in-side-window` call in `warbo-show-pi-chat` (`personal/warbo-llm.el`).

Diagnosis via `emacs_eval`: the side window had `window-side=bottom` and `window-slot=0` set correctly, but `dedicated=nil`, so `display-buffer` was free to reuse it. Making it dedicated prevents that.

Also applied the fix to the already-open side window immediately via `set-window-dedicated-p`.
